title: Chalk 1.3.3 (2017 Export Wav)
lyrics:
You won't go foolin’ me twice now, baby
I'm sorry, that's the way it is, yeah
I let you get to me once now, baby
But I’ll never let you in again
Cover it up, you like to play your own game
Cover it up, don't let them know what you're thinkin'
I bet you never tell them how it feels
I bet you never even tried to be real
